The format of the news file is very easy, just follow the simple rules below
and you will be making headline news in no time. :-)

The format is important to follow exactly like shown in the example NEWS.TXT.

Line
1      : Date..                        Max 6 characters   Today/01-Jan/010194
2      : Short description             Max 29 characters
3      : News text
4      : News text
5      : News text
6      : News text
X      : /***/                         End of news marker

Example:

01-Jan                               <---------- Line 1 in NEWS.TXT
Happy New Year

  We wish you a Happy New Year

/***/
                 <------------- Next news item starts on this line

In the News text you can insert colour codes like this.

  We wish you a %014Happy%007 New Year

This would make 'Happy' turn yellow. The codes can be obtained from the
color selection menu inside Terminate.

